title: Brooklyn Navy Yard’s Annual Open House
description: Join the Brooklyn Navy Yard for their Annual Open House on Saturday, October 18— a free celebration of makers, creativity, and community. Visit the Yard from 12-5 PM and get behind-the-scenes access to over 35 trailblazing Brooklyn-based businesses in fashion, design, technology, and more. Participate in hands-on demos, exclusive tours, timed programs and enjoy on-site food trucks and live entertainment all in one dynamic space!
